04-28T22:36:47.000Z","msg":"去深水埗d手工店搵吓有冇好似呢張圖，好似羊毛咁嘅材料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDmxDDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDmxDDK.jpg&h=2c402c41&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n然後買要有好細嘅倒勾嘅針<br />\n咁先可以拮到<br />\n<a href=\"https://woolwoolfelt.com/2017/09/27/%E3%80%90%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%98%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8A%E6%AF%9B%E6%B0%88%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%87%9D%E6%B0%88%E5%9F%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwoolwoolfelt.com%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%25A4%258E%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%2598%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258A%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25B0%2588%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2587%259D%25E6%25B0%2588%25E5%259F%25BA%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImIGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=3621ffb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://woolwoolfelt.com/2017/09/27/%E3%80%90%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%98%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8A%E6%AF%9B%E6%B0%88%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%87%9D%E6%B0%88%E5%9F%BA/</a><br />\n有關針可以睇呢個<br />\n假眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XfuF0x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XfuF0x.jpg&h=bad4ff4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後開始拮<br />\n要攞舊發泡膠(最好攞舊厚身d嘅)<br />\n將白羊毛放上去拮比較安全<br />\n拮左D白色嘅羊毛氈先<br />\n拮到佢結埋一舊、D毛入左去<br />\n硬硬地之後<br />\n你就可以再拮D粉紅色羊毛氈上去<br />\n同上，D毛入晒去白色羊毛氈球之後<br />\n之後就可以整耳仔了<br />\n整耳仔要攞一條仔粉紅色羊毛<br />\n然後對摺<br />\n變做長條狀<br />\n再拮吓佢<br />\n記住上下都要拮<br />\n拮好之後<br />\n放喺你要嘅位<br />\n之後打斜拮，記住<br />\n(唔好拮親手。拮到好撚痛)<br />\n之後就係眼<br />\n你要將支針好似見到popo咁<br />\n好嬲咁大力咁一野拮入去<br />\n拮左個窿<br />\n之後就放隻假眼入去<br />\n鼻就將舊紅色嘅羊毛氈卷埋一舊<br />\n再拮上去佢嘅面上<br />\n而鼻窿就用細粒嘅黑色羊毛氈拮入去鼻入面<br />\n最後到嘴<br />\n亦都係最難嘅part<br />\n因為要拮條黑色嘅細線入去<br />\n你眼力一定要好好<br />\n要拮條線嘅中間、頭同埋尾<br />\n之後你就可以<br />\n加番呢條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tae7uj8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTae7uj8.jpg&h=86d9bb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係先用針由頭上面狠狠地拮落下面<br />\n之後放入去<br />\n如果仲睇到支嘢<br />\n可以加番D粉紅羊毛氈上去<br />\n補吓佢 <br />\n之後扣返條電話繩<br />\n就完成了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9917fa1bc9a901cb181f87861c4fb480aa476fe7","tid":1993352,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T22:59:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2281a3795a73ba1e27b124bbf784e5e0fb498d","tid":1993352,"uid":186708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T23:17:10.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a857df91019032919a8bffb3017f861702171d","tid":1993352,"uid":345137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af551231372666a86b00ec87523b3a96b4252042","tid":1993352,"uid":66987,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7d4535b17fdc2d11f104755cd67ba8664f074856","tid":1993352,"uid":345137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"超打意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點整?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T22:36:47.000Z","msg":"去深水埗d手工店搵吓有冇好似呢張圖，好似羊毛咁嘅材料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDmxDDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDmxDDK.jpg&h=2c402c41&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n然後買要有好細嘅